data.name: kryptonLabel.Values.Text
data.value:
Hover the mouse over the Quick Access Toolbar buttons in see simple text ToolTips which show just a single line of text.
Hover over the Application Button or the Clipboard group of buttons to see ToolTips that have a title and body sections.
Hovering over the Include group of buttons will show ToolTips that have a title, body and image in combination.
